KR-Housing-LongRAG-Bench — License
==================================

Scope
-----
This repository contains two distinct kinds of material with different terms:

1. BENCHMARK ANNOTATIONS (this project's own work) — the QA labels, questions,
   answers, evidence locators, gold predicates, page/cell/row ids, split and
   provider/region metadata, context-bundle references, documentation, and all
   evaluation / build / verification code under scripts/.

2. UNDERLYING SOURCE MATERIALS — the original housing announcements
   (입주자모집공고), public tabular data (e.g. MOLIT 실거래, HUG 분양이력), and
   statute/rule texts that the annotations point to. These are NOT redistributed
   in this repository; only locators (source URLs, page/cell/row ids) and short
   factual excerpts are included.


